  "title": "Tapping for wealth fits me",
  "subtitle": "A five-minute tapping script for releasing the belief that wealth will make your life more complicated rather than more supported.",
  "excerpt": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 26 of the MONEY program. The script works with the specific fear that more money means more stress, more to manage, more to protect, more to lose.",
