  "sourceNotes": "Adapted from Day 26 of MONEY: A 12-Week Tapping Program (Rebecca J Page, 2025), \"Trust that wealth fits my lifestyle.\" Tapping framework: Gary Craig's Emotional Freedom Technique (EFT), building on Roger Callahan's Thought Field Therapy.",
